TI  - Effectiveness and Safety of Methods to Prevent Bloodstream and Other Infections and Noninfectious Complications Associated With Peripherally Inserted Central Catheters: A Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis.
AU  - Dobrescu A
AU  - Constantin AM
AU  - Pinte L
AU  - Chapman A
AU  - Ratajczak P
AU  - Klerings I
