TI  - Intravascular Ultrasound Assessment of Distal Trans-Radial Access in Patients Undergoing Percutaneous Coronary Intervention.
AU  - Poletti E
AU  - Colletti G
AU  - Zivelonghi C
AU  - Benedetti A
AU  - Moroni A
