TI  - Novel cannulation strategy with a bidirectional cannula for distal limb perfusion during peripheral veno-arterial extracorporeal life support: A preliminary, single-centre study.
AU  - Simons J
AU  - Doddema AR
AU  - Korver EP
AU  - di Mauro M
AU  - Agricola S
AU  - Smets J
AU  - Metz R
AU  - Mariani S
