TI  - Complications and Practice Variation in the Use of Peripherally Inserted Central Venous Catheters in People With Cystic Fibrosis: The Prospective Study of Peripherally Inserted Venous Catheters in People With Cystic Fibrosis Study.
AU  - Gifford AH
AU  - Hinton AC
AU  - Jia S
AU  - Nasr SZ
AU  - Mermis JD
AU  - Lahiri T
AU  - Zemanick ET
AU  - Teneback CC
